      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>\n  .why-section {\n    background: #f0efe8;\n    padding: 64px 24px;\n    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n    text-align: center;\n    max-width: 680px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n  .why-badge {\n    display: inline-block;\n    background: #f5c842;\n    color: #111;\n    font-size: 12px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    letter-spacing: 0.12em;\n    padding: 8px 20px;\n    border-radius: 999px;\n    margin-bottom: 24px;\n  }\n  .why-heading {\n    font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 46px);\n    font-weight: 900;\n    color: #111;\n    margin: 0 0 20px;\n    line-height: 1.15;\n    letter-spacing: -0.02em;\n  }\n  .why-para {\n    font-size: clamp(15px, 2.5vw, 17px);\n    color: #666;\n    line-height: 1.75;\n    max-width: 520px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"why-section\">\n  <div class=\"why-badge\">WHY IT WORKS</div>\n  <h2 class=\"why-heading\">Your skin already knows what it needs. We just gave it that.</h2>\n  <p class=\"why-para\">Most moisturisers are 70% water with synthetic fillers — they sit on the surface, evaporate, and do nothing. Beef tallow is molecularly identical to your skin's natural oil. It absorbs completely, rebuilds your barrier, and works at the cellular level with vitamins A, D, E and K. Four ingredients. No BS. Real results.</p>\n</div>",
