      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n  .tl-section {\n    background: #f0efe8;\n    padding: 56px 20px;\n    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  .tl-badge {\n    display: inline-block;\n    background: #f5c842;\n    color: #111;\n    font-size: 12px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    letter-spacing: 0.12em;\n    padding: 8px 20px;\n    border-radius: 999px;\n    margin-bottom: 16px;\n  }\n  .tl-heading {\n    font-size: clamp(28px, 6vw, 48px);\n    font-weight: 900;\n    color: #111;\n    margin-bottom: 40px;\n    letter-spacing: -0.02em;\n    line-height: 1.1;\n  }\n  .tl-tabs {\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: center;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    border-bottom: 1.5px solid #ddd;\n    max-width: 860px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n  .tl-tab {\n    background: none;\n    border: none;\n    border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;\n    padding: clamp(8px, 2vw, 12px) clamp(8px, 2.5vw, 18px);\n    font-size: clamp(9px, 1.8vw, 12px);\n    font-weight: 800;\n    letter-spacing: 0.1em;\n    color: #aaa;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    margin-bottom: -1.5px;\n    transition: color 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n  }\n  .tl-tab.active {\n    color: #111;\n    border-bottom-color: #f5c842;\n  }\n  .tl-panels {\n    max-width: 860px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n  .tl-panel {\n    display: none;\n    background: #fff;\n    border-radius: 0 0 16px 16px;\n    padding: clamp(20px, 4vw, 40px) clamp(18px, 4vw, 36px);\n    text-align: left;\n    gap: clamp(20px, 4vw, 40px);\n    align-items: stretch;\n  }\n  .tl-panel.active {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n  }\n  .tl-left {\n    flex: 1 1 260px;\n    min-width: 0;\n  }\n  .tl-right {\n    flex: 1 1 220px;\n    min-width: 0;\n  }\n  .tl-title {\n    font-size: clamp(18px, 3.5vw, 24px);\n    font-weight: 900;\n    color: #111;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n    letter-spacing: -0.01em;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n  }\n  .tl-desc {\n    font-size: clamp(13px, 2vw, 15px);\n    color: #888;\n    line-height: 1.7;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n  }\n  .tl-point {\n    font-size: clamp(13px, 2vw, 15px);\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #111;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: flex-start;\n    gap: 8px;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n  }\n  .tl-point::before {\n    content: '→';\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    color: #111;\n  }\n  .tl-quote-box {\n    background: #fdf9e3;\n    border-left: 4px solid #f5c842;\n    border-radius: 12px;\n    padding: clamp(18px, 3vw, 28px) clamp(16px, 3vw, 24px);\n    height: 100%;\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    justify-content: center;\n  }\n  .tl-quote {\n    font-size: clamp(14px, 2.5vw, 18px);\n    font-weight: 800;\n    color: #111;\n    line-height: 1.5;\n    margin-bottom: 14px;\n    letter-spacing: -0.01em;\n  }\n  .tl-author {\n    font-size: clamp(12px, 1.8vw, 14px);\n    color: #999;\n    font-weight: 500;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"tl-section\">\n  <div class=\"tl-badge\">WHAT TO EXPECT</div>\n  <h2 class=\"tl-heading\">Your Skin. Day By Day.</h2>\n\n  <div class=\"tl-tabs\" id=\"tlTabs\">\n    <button class=\"tl-tab active\" data-tab=\"0\">DAY 1</button>\n    <button class=\"tl-tab\" data-tab=\"1\">DAY 3</button>\n    <button class=\"tl-tab\" data-tab=\"2\">WEEK 1</button>\n    <button class=\"tl-tab\" data-tab=\"3\">MONTH 1</button>\n    <button class=\"tl-tab\" data-tab=\"4\">MONTH 3</button>\n    <button class=\"tl-tab\" data-tab=\"5\">ONGOING</button>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"tl-panels\">\n\n    <div class=\"tl-panel active\" data-panel=\"0\">\n      <div class=\"tl-left\">\n        <p class=\"tl-title\">First Application</p>\n        <p class=\"tl-desc\">Beef tallow begins absorbing immediately — no greasy residue, no sitting on the surface. Your skin recognises it from the first use.</p>\n        <div class=\"tl-point\">Skin feels immediately more hydrated</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-point\">Tightness and dryness start to ease</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-point\">Absorbs completely — no film left behind</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"tl-right\">\n        <div class=\"tl-quote-box\">\n          <p class=\"tl-quote\">\"Wasn't expecting it to absorb that fast. Felt different straight away.\"</p>\n          <p class=\"tl-author\">— Karim, 44</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tl-panel\" data-panel=\"1\">\n      <div class=\"tl-left\">\n        <p class=\"tl-title\">Skin Barrier Repair Begins</p>\n        <p class=\"tl-desc\">Raw honey's antibacterial properties activate. Beeswax creates a breathable protective layer. Redness and irritation start calming down.</p>\n        <div class=\"tl-point\">Redness visibly reduced</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-point\">Skin feels noticeably calmer</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-point\">First signs of natural glow returning</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"tl-right\">\n        <div class=\"tl-quote-box\">\n          <p class=\"tl-quote\">\"The burning stopped by day three. I hadn't had a day without it in years.\"</p>\n          <p class=\"tl-author\">— Charbel, 52</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tl-panel\" data-panel=\"2\">\n      <div class=\"tl-left\">\n        <p class=\"tl-title\">Visible Skin Renewal</p>\n        <p class=\"tl-desc\">Vitamins A, D, E and K begin supporting cell turnover. Fine lines start to soften. Skin texture improves noticeably to the touch.</p>\n        <div class=\"tl-point\">Fine lines visibly softer</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-point\">Skin texture smoother to touch</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-point\">Complexion looks more even and awake</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"tl-right\">\n        <div class=\"tl-quote-box\">\n          <p class=\"tl-quote\">\"After a week my wife said I looked different. She couldn't figure out what it was.\"</p>\n          <p class=\"tl-author\">— Rami, 41</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tl-panel\" data-panel=\"3\">\n      <div class=\"tl-left\">\n        <p class=\"tl-title\">Transformation Starts Showing</p>\n        <p class=\"tl-desc\">Skin barrier is rebuilding. Sebum production starts balancing. Sun damage begins fading. People around you start noticing before you mention anything.</p>\n        <div class=\"tl-point\">Wrinkles and fine lines noticeably reduced</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-point\">Sun damage and dark spots fading</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-point\">People start noticing before you say anything</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"tl-right\">\n        <div class=\"tl-quote-box\">\n          <p class=\"tl-quote\">\"Someone accused me of getting Botox at 30 days. I've never touched it.\"</p>\n          <p class=\"tl-author\">— Georges, 48</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tl-panel\" data-panel=\"4\">\n      <div class=\"tl-left\">\n        <p class=\"tl-title\">Your Skin Is Healing Itself</p>\n        <p class=\"tl-desc\">The skin barrier is fully restored. Your skin is now producing and regulating its own oils properly — the way it was designed to before synthetic products disrupted it.</p>\n        <div class=\"tl-point\">Skin looks years younger</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-point\">Chronic irritation, redness, dryness — gone</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-point\">Confidence in your appearance returns</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"tl-right\">\n        <div class=\"tl-quote-box\">\n          <p class=\"tl-quote\">\"Three months in and I look better than I did at 35. The Beirut sun had destroyed my skin. Not anymore.\"</p>\n          <p class=\"tl-author\">— Elie, 54</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"tl-panel\" data-panel=\"5\">\n      <div class=\"tl-left\">\n        <p class=\"tl-title\">A New Version Of Your Skin</p>\n        <p class=\"tl-desc\">Men who continue using LEGACARE report their skin keeps improving gradually and naturally. The longer you use it, the better it gets. Most never go back.</p>\n        <div class=\"tl-point\">Skin that gets compliments without explanation</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-point\">A face that matches how you actually feel</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-point\">2,000+ men never went back to anything else</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"tl-right\">\n        <div class=\"tl-quote-box\">\n          <p class=\"tl-quote\">\"I'm on my fourth jar. My friends in Beirut all switched after seeing my skin.\"</p>\n          <p class=\"tl-author\">— Fadi, 58</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\n  document.getElementById('tlTabs').addEventListener('click', function(e) {\n    const tab = e.target.closest('.tl-tab');\n    if (!tab) return;\n    const idx = tab.dataset.tab;\n    document.querySelectorAll('.tl-tab').forEach(t => t.classList.remove('active'));\n    document.querySelectorAll('.tl-panel').forEach(p => p.classList.remove('active'));\n    tab.classList.add('active');\n    document.querySelector('.tl-panel[data-panel=\"' + idx + '\"]').classList.add('active');\n  });\n</script>",
