    "custom_liquid_PyWqQE": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "t:sections.custom-liquid.presets.name",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }\n  .faq-section {\n    background: #f0efe8;\n    padding: 64px 24px;\n    font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  .faq-heading {\n    font-size: clamp(22px, 5vw, 40px);\n    font-weight: 900;\n    color: #111;\n    letter-spacing: -0.01em;\n    margin-bottom: 14px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n  }\n  .faq-sub {\n    font-size: 15px;\n    color: #888;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    max-width: 560px;\n    margin: 0 auto 48px;\n  }\n  .faq-list {\n    max-width: 720px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    text-align: left;\n  }\n  .faq-item {\n    border-top: 1px solid #ddd;\n    background: transparent;\n  }\n  .faq-item:last-child {\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;\n  }\n  .faq-question {\n    width: 100%;\n    background: transparent;\n    border: none;\n    display: flex;\n    justify-content: space-between;\n    align-items: center;\n    padding: 20px 4px;\n    cursor: pointer;\n    gap: 16px;\n    text-align: left;\n  }\n  .faq-question span {\n    font-size: 15px;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: #111;\n    line-height: 1.4;\n    flex: 1;\n  }\n  .faq-icon {\n    font-size: 22px;\n    font-weight: 300;\n    color: #111;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n    line-height: 1;\n    transition: transform 0.25s;\n    width: 24px;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  .faq-item.open .faq-icon {\n    transform: rotate(45deg);\n  }\n  .faq-item.open .faq-question {\n    background: #ece9e0;\n    padding-left: 12px;\n    padding-right: 12px;\n    border-radius: 4px 4px 0 0;\n  }\n  .faq-answer {\n    display: none;\n    font-size: 14px;\n    color: #555;\n    line-height: 1.75;\n    padding: 16px 12px 22px;\n    background: #ece9e0;\n    border-radius: 0 0 4px 4px;\n  }\n  .faq-item.open .faq-answer {\n    display: block;\n  }\n</style>\n\n<div class=\"faq-section\">\n  <h2 class=\"faq-heading\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n  <p class=\"faq-sub\">We understand that investing in your skin is a big decision. That's why we're here to help you make an informed choice.</p>\n\n  <div class=\"faq-list\" id=\"faqList\">\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item open\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">\n        <span>What ingredients are in the Tallow Balm?</span>\n        <div class=\"faq-icon\">+</div>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        Only 4 natural ingredients: grass-fed, grass-finished beef tallow, cold-pressed organic olive oil, organic manuka honey, and organic beeswax. No fillers, no chemicals — just raw, unadulterated skin nutrition that helps your skin thrive naturally.\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">\n        <span>Do your products contain any artificial fragrances?</span>\n        <div class=\"faq-icon\">+</div>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        No — completely free from artificial fragrances. Any scent comes naturally from the ingredients themselves. This makes it ideal for those with sensitivities to synthetic fragrances or anyone seeking truly natural skincare.\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">\n        <span>Is this suitable for sensitive skin?</span>\n        <div class=\"faq-icon\">+</div>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        Yes. The natural fat profile in grass-fed tallow closely resembles human skin cells, making it highly compatible and gentle. Many customers with eczema, rosacea, and other skin sensitivities report significant improvements after switching to this balm.\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">\n        <span>Does the balm have a smell?</span>\n        <div class=\"faq-icon\">+</div>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        The Unscented version has a very light, natural scent from the pure ingredients — no added fragrance. Most people describe it as neutral and barely noticeable once applied. If you choose Citrus or Lavender, the scent comes only from natural essential oils — gentle, clean, and never overpowering.\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">\n        <span>How do I apply the Tallow Balm?</span>\n        <div class=\"faq-icon\">+</div>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        Take a small amount — about the size of a pea for the face — and warm it between your fingertips. It melts slightly with body heat, making it easy to spread. Gently massage into clean skin using upward, circular motions until fully absorbed. A little goes a long way.\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">\n        <span>How often should I use it?</span>\n        <div class=\"faq-icon\">+</div>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        For best results, use 1–2 times daily on clean skin. Most men use it morning and night. Those with very dry skin may benefit from more frequent application, while those with oilier skin might prefer once daily — typically in the evening.\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">\n        <span>Can I use the Tallow Balm on my face?</span>\n        <div class=\"faq-icon\">+</div>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        Absolutely. Its natural composition mirrors human skin cells, making it ideal for facial use. It's deeply moisturising without clogging pores and helps balance oil production, reduce fine lines, and soothe irritation.\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">\n        <span>Will this cause breakouts?</span>\n        <div class=\"faq-icon\">+</div>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        No. Grass-fed beef tallow is bioidentical to human sebum — your pores recognise it and absorb it completely. Unlike synthetic oils that sit on the surface, tallow penetrates naturally and is non-comedogenic. Many customers with acne-prone or oily skin actually report clearer skin after switching from conventional moisturisers.\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">\n        <span>What is your return policy?</span>\n        <div class=\"faq-icon\">+</div>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        We offer a 90-Day Results Guarantee — not a standard return window. If you don't see visible improvement within 90 days of consistent use, contact us and we'll refund every cent. No questions asked. No return required. You don't even need to send the jar back.\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"faq-item\">\n      <button class=\"faq-question\">\n        <span>When will I receive my order?</span>\n        <div class=\"faq-icon\">+</div>\n      </button>\n      <div class=\"faq-answer\">\n        All orders are processed and shipped within 1–2 business days. Once shipped, you'll receive a tracking link automatically. Estimated delivery is 3–5 business days. No hidden fees or surprise charges at checkout.\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<script>\n  document.getElementById('faqList').addEventListener('click', function(e) {\n    const btn = e.target.closest('.faq-question');\n    if (!btn) return;\n    const item = btn.closest('.faq-item');\n    const isOpen = item.classList.contains('open');\n    document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(i => i.classList.remove('open'));\n    if (!isOpen) item.classList.add('open');\n  });\n</script>",
